<br>
Other Possibilities:<br>
Crested Spaulders:  11AC, 5sta<br>
Selling the LSoEE for FB and Cash<br>
I would also say some of the 2ac, 35hps earrings, or even better and if you have the cash, buy the things you need for your PoTC earring.<br>
Or I would finally suggest some cobalt gauntlets.  I'm sure you can find someone selling them for cheap.  Good AC, crap effect.<br>
